reviewText: This was VERY disappointing! It comes straight out of the movie "Seventeen Miracles," which I absolutely love. I thought this would add some depth or information to her story, but it doesn't. If you've seen "Seventeen Miracles" you have already seen it all. If you haven't seen "Seventeen Miracles" then buy it instead. This was a complete waste of money.
